{"tid":1865758,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]關於紅猴","createTime":"2020-02-06T10:55:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T11:13:44.000Z","uid":339261,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"79ac34468b01036f06b25a0de6d917c281cd42de","tid":1865758,"uid":339261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T10:55:35.000Z","msg":"1.紅猴是日行性的動物，通常生活在乾燥的大草原及稀疏的林地，主要在地面活動，是地棲程度最高的靈長類動物；牠們會不時地用後腳站立向四周瞭望，發現危險的時候，會躲到樹上，或快速逃走。<br />\n<br />\n2.紅猴是跑得最快的靈長類動物，時速可達55公里。<br />\n<br />\n3.紅猴是群居的動物，每一群平均有15隻成員，包括一隻成年雄性的領導者，與2-8隻成年雌猴。雄猴大部分的時間會用樹木或白蟻塚當做瞭望台，擔負起保衛妻小的責任。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zE90bGg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzE90bGg.jpg&h=d961ab16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jhjCYmh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjhjCYmh.jpg&h=394863a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OQtwimi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOQtwimi.jpg&h=29a01609&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ckECYmj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FckECYmj.jpg&h=0254b3db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZSMayUG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZSMayUG.jpg&h=3a956018&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g1UCYmn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg1UCYmn.jpg&h=a07f8e91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QWLFV73.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQWLFV73.jpg&h=65cf894d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7bfcc30bf2498aea7aa73fffff5fe1e6e93c3a02","tid":1865758,"uid":339261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:13:25.000Z","msg":"俗        名： 紅猴<br />\n英        文： Patas Monkey<br />\n學        名： Erythrocebus patas<br />\n分        類： 脊索動物門,哺乳綱,靈長目,獼猴科<br />\n保育等級： 暫無危機 LC<br />\n館        區： 非洲動物區"},{"pid":"463ef6719797e1509c2e3e6ed78431d4b9ce6a87","tid":1865758,"uid":339261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:13:44.000Z","msg":"背側為紅色略帶灰色，雄性比較偏紅色，腹側則為灰白色、淡橙色或紅褐色，腿部顏色比較淡，尾巴前段顏色較深，後段較淺；成年雄性自頸部到肩部的毛比較長，有點兒像馬的鬃毛，臉部有白色的鬍鬚；幼猴幾乎全身都是紅色，身軀及四肢修長。"}]}